#

Grilled Chicken with Roasted Vegetables

45 min
$15
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

EasyHealthyGrilled

Description

Juicy grilled chicken served alongside a medley of roasted seasonal vegetables, drizzled with a light balsamic glaze.

Ingredients

  • chicken breast: 2 pieces
  • bell peppers: 1 cup
  • zucchini: 1 medium
  • carrots: 1 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • balsamic glaze: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • italian seasoning: 1 teaspoon
